- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper analyzes the behavior of communication groups in mobile messaging systems such as WhatsApp.
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also likely as the paper analyzes the content of messages in WhatsApp groups, including the use of multimedia content and emojis.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is another possible category as the paper focuses on political discussions in public groups, which has implications for society and politics.
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper introduces a framework and metrics to characterize the behavior of communication groups in mobile messaging systems.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also less likely but possible as the paper analyzes the use of multimedia content in WhatsApp messages.
